title: Did the student newspaper John Hopkins withdraw an article alleging the death of CAVID-19 "not unusual "?
subtitle: The story reportedly calls into question the accuracy and credibility of the reported COVID-19 deaths in the United States.
author: Madison Dapcevich
vclaim: An article entitled "Convid-19 Death: A View of United States Data" was published in the student-run John Hopkins newspaper in November 2020, and then retracted.
